1
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:30,030
[Youthful Glory]

2
00:01:30,110 --> 00:01:32,860
[Episode 1]

3
00:01:36,880 --> 00:01:38,920
The Duke of Ling's family and
the Marquis of Jing'an's family

4
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:40,520
are to be united in marriage!

5
00:01:43,160 --> 00:01:44,640
Hurry up now, move quickly.

6
00:01:43,620 --> 00:01:47,110
[Marquis of Jing'an's Mansion]

7
00:01:45,880 --> 00:01:47,680
Don't miss the auspicious time.

8
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:49,720
Be careful, steady now!

9
00:01:50,080 --> 00:01:51,479
These items are very precious!

10
00:01:51,479 --> 00:01:52,800
Look at that jade ruyi scepter!

11
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:53,720
The Fourth Miss of the Ming family

12
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:55,200
is the foremost noble lady in the capital.

13
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:56,280
Her father, the Marquis of Jing'an,

14
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:58,100
holds military authority over the Yangxi Prefecture.

15
00:01:58,100 --> 00:02:00,100
Such grand fanfare is only fitting.

16
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:08,210
[Harmony and Abundance]

17
00:02:08,250 --> 00:02:09,840
A fine match,

18
00:02:09,919 --> 00:02:11,930
a perfect union to be!

19
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:16,190
Great joy for the household of the Marquis of Jing'an!

20
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:17,240
My Lady,

21
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:18,000
the Duchess of Ling

22
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:19,560
has arrived with the betrothal gifts.

23
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:20,320
No rush.

24
00:02:20,690 --> 00:02:21,820
Let her wait a while.

25
00:02:22,210 --> 00:02:24,440
This is the Duchess of Ling?

26
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:26,600
Your Grace, please mind your step.

27
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:28,079
Who else could it be?

28
00:02:27,940 --> 00:02:31,030
[Li Lingyi, Duchess of Ling]

29
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:30,440
Such a grand display.

30
00:02:30,440 --> 00:02:31,120
She clearly wants

31
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,650
the entire capital to know

32
00:02:32,720 --> 00:02:34,810
that her family and the Ming family
will soon become in-laws.

33
00:02:32,930 --> 00:02:39,070
[Marquis of Jing'an's Mansion]

34
00:02:34,920 --> 00:02:36,520
Anyone would do the same

35
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:38,960
when becoming family with the Marquis of Jing'an.

36
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:39,760
My Lady,

37
00:02:39,840 --> 00:02:42,079
are you really going to accept this marriage?

38
00:02:42,079 --> 00:02:43,410
Who said I would accept?

39
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:44,600
The Liang family's intentions in proposing

40
00:02:44,600 --> 00:02:46,200
this match are far from pure.

41
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:47,240
They're clearly coveting

42
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:48,680
Father's military power.

43
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:49,520
Besides, Liang Zixuan

44
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:50,600
has long been intimately involved

45
00:02:50,600 --> 00:02:51,520
with his own cousin sister,

46
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:53,000
even secretly getting her pregnant.

47
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:54,920
If I were to agree to this marriage,

48
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:56,920
I would be completely out of my mind.

49
00:02:58,530 --> 00:03:02,490
[Ming Tan, Fourth Daughter of the Marquis of Jing'an]

50
00:03:05,260 --> 00:03:07,320
These pairs of shoes are from Tongsheng Shop.

51
00:03:07,320 --> 00:03:08,290
The shopkeeper said

52
00:03:08,290 --> 00:03:10,180
that you have impeccable taste, My Lady.

53
00:03:10,180 --> 00:03:13,080
Whatever you wear becomes the trend in the capital.

54
00:03:11,310 --> 00:03:13,320
[Suxin, Maid of the Zhaoshui House]

55
00:03:13,350 --> 00:03:15,240
He's waiting to see which pair you'll choose

56
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:17,370
so they can make more in the same style.

57
00:03:23,480 --> 00:03:25,579
Although the embroidery is exquisite,

58
00:03:25,579 --> 00:03:27,170
the fabric is limp

59
00:03:27,190 --> 00:03:28,320
and lacks firmness,

60
00:03:28,930 --> 00:03:30,450
not top-tier brocade.

61
00:03:31,270 --> 00:03:33,360
And the pearls adorning the toes,

62
00:03:34,110 --> 00:03:35,430
though large and full,

63
00:03:35,490 --> 00:03:36,890
lack luster

64
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:38,760
and certainly are not the sea pearls

65
00:03:38,760 --> 00:03:40,490
the shopkeeper boasted about.

66
00:03:41,650 --> 00:03:42,250
Whatever.

67
00:03:42,530 --> 00:03:44,180
I'll take this pair with the cloud pattern.

68
00:03:44,180 --> 00:03:45,910
Though simpler in appearance,

69
00:03:46,310 --> 00:03:48,770
the silk thread used is of superior quality.

70
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:52,710
Girl, could I trouble you

71
00:03:52,710 --> 00:03:54,120
to go and announce us again?

72
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:56,079
If the Fourth Miss still doesn't come,

73
00:03:56,079 --> 00:03:57,880
we'll miss the auspicious time.

74
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:59,360
The Fourth Miss is still getting dressed.

75
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:00,590
Please wait a little longer, Your Grace.

76
00:04:00,590 --> 00:04:02,430
Is that all you can say?

77
00:04:03,920 --> 00:04:05,650
Making Your Grace wait for so long...

78
00:04:05,650 --> 00:04:07,140
is my fault.

79
00:04:07,410 --> 00:04:08,470
It doesn't matter.

80
00:04:08,640 --> 00:04:10,040
It's just a short while.

81
00:04:10,560 --> 00:04:11,820
Let me take a good look.

82
00:04:11,920 --> 00:04:14,200
Our Ming Tan is as beautiful as a flower,

83
00:04:14,220 --> 00:04:15,240
cultured, and graceful.

84
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:16,440
Such a good girl.

85
00:04:16,640 --> 00:04:19,390
Of course, we must hurry and welcome her into our family.

86
00:04:19,390 --> 00:04:20,420
This marriage

87
00:04:20,440 --> 00:04:22,440
was long decided by Chancellor Su,

88
00:04:22,470 --> 00:04:24,340
with jade pendants exchanged as tokens.

89
00:04:24,340 --> 00:04:27,070
Your Grace doesn't need to worry about anything.

90
00:04:29,250 --> 00:04:31,180
Fourth Miss, here is the list of betrothal gifts.

91
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:29,730
[Betrothal Gift List]

92
00:04:29,770 --> 00:04:30,290
[Betrothal Letter]

93
00:04:31,280 --> 00:04:32,340
Please take a look.

94
00:04:43,170 --> 00:04:45,100
How generous you are.

95
00:04:45,730 --> 00:04:47,190
I'm so lucky

96
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:48,760
to receive such favor

97
00:04:48,760 --> 00:04:50,360
from both His Grace and Your Grace.

98
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:51,159
Ming Tan,

99
00:04:51,440 --> 00:04:53,640
you deserve all the best.

100
00:04:54,450 --> 00:04:56,080
That's why everyone says

101
00:04:56,080 --> 00:04:57,940
you were born with good fortune, Fourth Miss.

102
00:04:57,940 --> 00:04:59,830
In all my years as a matchmaker,

103
00:04:59,860 --> 00:05:00,850
this is the first time I've seen

104
00:05:00,850 --> 00:05:02,310
a groom's family in the capital

105
00:05:02,310 --> 00:05:04,870
be... so lavish!

106
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:09,600
So it was all arranged by you?

107
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:10,440
Yes.

108
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:12,760
That explains it.

109
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:22,250
These pieces of jewelry

110
00:05:22,440 --> 00:05:24,100
are all from Cuojin Pavilion,

111
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:24,920
not from the capital's

112
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:26,450
renowned Wanzhu Pavilion.

113
00:05:27,070 --> 00:05:28,300
And these bolts of cloth

114
00:05:28,300 --> 00:05:29,990
are also last year's brocades,

115
00:05:29,990 --> 00:05:32,360
no longer fashionable in the capital.

116
00:05:35,280 --> 00:05:37,080
Such deceptionâ€”passing off the fake as the real

117
00:05:37,080 --> 00:05:39,200
and filling in with second-rate goods.

118
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:39,960
I guess

119
00:05:39,960 --> 00:05:42,290
quite a bit was skimmed off the top, right?

120
00:05:42,409 --> 00:05:44,980
Fourth Miss, I wouldn't dare do such a thing.

121
00:05:45,010 --> 00:05:45,970
I wouldn't dare.

122
00:05:47,460 --> 00:05:48,220
Your Grace.

123
00:05:48,840 --> 00:05:50,620
It's not that I'm being picky.

124
00:05:51,100 --> 00:05:53,020
But betrothal gifts

125
00:05:53,050 --> 00:05:54,190
carry deep significanceâ€”

126
00:05:54,190 --> 00:05:56,190
they symbolize blessings for

127
00:05:56,220 --> 00:05:57,580
a harmonious marriage.

128
00:05:58,460 --> 00:06:00,260
But today's betrothal gifts...

129
00:06:02,280 --> 00:06:03,560
Those who know might say

130
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:05,960
the matchmaker didn't do her job properly.

131
00:06:05,970 --> 00:06:07,090
But those who don't

132
00:06:08,080 --> 00:06:09,240
might think I'm

133
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:10,760
reaching above my station

134
00:06:10,780 --> 00:06:12,910
and not welcomed by my future in-laws.

135
00:06:13,300 --> 00:06:14,090
Ming Tan.

136
00:06:13,870 --> 00:06:15,260
[Betrothal Gift List]

137
00:06:14,860 --> 00:06:15,660
Ming Tan.

138
00:06:16,320 --> 00:06:18,020
Don't say that.

139
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:18,880
Later,

140
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:21,840
I'll personally prepare a proper set of betrothal gifts again

141
00:06:21,840 --> 00:06:24,000
to ensure you don't suffer even the slightest grievance.

142
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:25,010
It's just

143
00:06:25,510 --> 00:06:26,920
that today, the entire capital

144
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:29,000
has witnessed me coming to present the betrothal gifts.

145
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:30,130
If it falls through,

146
00:06:31,130 --> 00:06:32,260
our Liang family...

147
00:06:33,280 --> 00:06:35,200
will be utterly humiliated.

148
00:06:37,130 --> 00:06:38,600
Please rest assured, Your Grace.

149
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:41,530
Our Ming family won't make things difficult for you.

150
00:06:44,140 --> 00:06:44,900
Here.

151
00:06:45,540 --> 00:06:46,420
[Betrothal Letter]

152
00:06:53,630 --> 00:06:55,320
[Betrothal Letter]

153
00:07:02,010 --> 00:07:04,210
[Betrothal Letter]

154
00:07:24,250 --> 00:07:25,720
What's happening?

155
00:07:25,570 --> 00:07:28,040
[Utmost Loyalty and Noble Integrity]

156
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:29,120
The betrothal goose has flown away, meaning
the couple will not grow old together.

157
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:30,920
This is a terrible omen, most inauspicious.

158
00:07:29,530 --> 00:07:31,240
[Ms. Zhang, Steward of the Marquis of Jing'an's Mansion]

159
00:07:32,110 --> 00:07:32,880
Ms. Zhang.

160
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:33,600
Your Grace.

161
00:07:33,620 --> 00:07:35,210
I'm young and inexperienced.

162
00:07:35,210 --> 00:07:36,409
What should we do now?

163
00:07:37,840 --> 00:07:38,860
I wonder if Your Grace

164
00:07:38,860 --> 00:07:39,680
has miscalculated the day and time

165
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:41,120
chosen for delivering the betrothal gifts.

166
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:42,520
-Well...
-How could this

167
00:07:42,520 --> 00:07:43,640
perfectly stable screen suddenly fall

168
00:07:43,640 --> 00:07:45,159
and frighten away the betrothal goose?

169
00:07:45,159 --> 00:07:46,790
It must be a sign from the heavens,

170
00:07:46,790 --> 00:07:48,250
warning us to avoid today.

171
00:07:48,840 --> 00:07:49,470
Well...

172
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:50,800
Although we have exchanged

173
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:51,810
the engagement tokens,

174
00:07:51,810 --> 00:07:53,120
the betrothal gifts are incomplete,

175
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:54,370
and the betrothal letter has been destroyed.

176
00:07:54,370 --> 00:07:55,440
Thus, today's betrothal ceremony

177
00:07:55,440 --> 00:07:56,720
cannot be counted.

178
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:58,440
Then...

179
00:08:00,770 --> 00:08:03,010
Although His Lordship is not in the capital,

180
00:08:03,010 --> 00:08:04,280
our Fourth Miss's marriage

181
00:08:04,280 --> 00:08:05,590
can't be taken lightly.

182
00:08:05,590 --> 00:08:07,920
Your Grace, please prepare the betrothal gifts again

183
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:10,520
and pick another auspicious time to send them.

184
00:08:16,960 --> 00:08:18,360
Will the Liang family truly not become

185
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:20,670
suspicious about our little trick just now?

186
00:08:20,670 --> 00:08:22,020
What if they do?

187
00:08:22,420 --> 00:08:24,310
Father will return to the capital soon.

188
00:08:24,310 --> 00:08:26,370
Why is the Liang family so impatient?

189
00:08:26,390 --> 00:08:28,280
It's all because they have something to hide.

190
00:08:28,280 --> 00:08:29,240
Young Master Liang has done

191
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:30,760
such a disgraceful thing,

192
00:08:30,780 --> 00:08:32,400
yet his family not only hides it

193
00:08:32,400 --> 00:08:34,799
but also comes here as if nothing happened.

194
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:36,919
They truly have no shame.

195
00:08:38,039 --> 00:08:38,840
Anyway,

196
00:08:39,400 --> 00:08:42,100
our Ming and Liang families are not of the same kind.

197
00:08:42,100 --> 00:08:43,340
I'll definitely...

198
00:08:44,760 --> 00:08:46,260
break off this engagement.

199
00:08:46,260 --> 00:08:47,360
My Lady!

200
00:08:48,400 --> 00:08:49,170
My Lady.

201
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:50,800
There's news from the Liang household.

202
00:08:50,740 --> 00:08:53,720
[Lyu'e, Maid of the Zhaoshui House]

203
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:52,600
Young Master Liang is taking his cousin

204
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:54,800
to Hanyan Temple to pray for blessings.

205
00:08:56,530 --> 00:08:57,860
Get the carriage ready.

206
00:09:42,920 --> 00:09:44,580
A curved knife for slaughter,

207
00:09:44,890 --> 00:09:46,390
aimed at the throat.

208
00:09:48,710 --> 00:09:50,390
You're from the Haiyou Sect.

209
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:54,000
In all of Xian, very few would dare to

210
00:09:54,750 --> 00:09:56,790
rob my army's supplies

211
00:09:56,210 --> 00:09:59,870
[Jiang Xu, Prince of Dingbei in Xian]

212
00:09:57,420 --> 00:10:00,080
and try to stop me from returning to the capital.

213
00:10:00,190 --> 00:10:03,320
The Liang family sent you?

214
00:10:03,630 --> 00:10:05,470
Go ask the King of Hell yourself!

215
00:10:05,640 --> 00:10:06,750
Kill him!

216
00:10:24,560 --> 00:10:26,150
It appears that you were badly wounded

217
00:10:26,150 --> 00:10:28,800
in the battle at Dongzhou, Prince of Dingbei.

218
00:11:24,650 --> 00:11:26,650
He's escaped toward Hanyan Temple!

219
00:11:26,920 --> 00:11:28,090
The Chief has ordered

220
00:11:28,090 --> 00:11:30,040
that he must not be allowed to enter the capital alive!

221
00:11:30,040 --> 00:11:31,240
-Yes, sir!
-Yes, sir!

222
00:11:48,240 --> 00:11:49,090
Be careful.

223
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:53,980
I've heard

224
00:11:54,040 --> 00:11:54,880
that wishes made at Huiji Hall

225
00:11:54,880 --> 00:11:56,400
often come true.

226
00:11:56,920 --> 00:11:58,440
Many women in the capital

227
00:11:58,460 --> 00:11:59,820
come here

228
00:11:59,920 --> 00:12:01,450
to pray for their children.

229
00:12:02,570 --> 00:12:05,100
I've been wanting to come here for a long time.

230
00:12:06,710 --> 00:12:10,230
[Liang Zixuan, Heir of the Duke of Ling]

231
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:10,820
It's all because Mother has watched me too closely.

232
00:12:10,970 --> 00:12:14,370
[Zhu'er, Liang Zixuan's Cousin]

233
00:12:12,270 --> 00:12:14,160
Mother's gone to the Ming family to offer betrothal gifts today.

234
00:12:14,160 --> 00:12:15,720
As long as we return before she does,

235
00:12:15,720 --> 00:12:16,520
we'll be fine.

236
00:12:20,200 --> 00:12:21,040
Zixuan.

237
00:12:21,880 --> 00:12:23,080
Choose a name

238
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:24,160
for our child.

239
00:12:37,340 --> 00:12:41,160
[Wish our child, Liang Wenting, peace and safety, blessed with
both happiness and wisdom; Liang Zixuan, Zhu'er]

240
00:12:45,800 --> 00:12:47,070
I've heard

241
00:12:47,160 --> 00:12:50,170
that the Fourth Miss Ming is picky about everything

242
00:12:50,530 --> 00:12:53,440
and especially harsh to the servants in her household.

243
00:12:53,440 --> 00:12:56,080
She must be difficult to get along with.

244
00:12:57,120 --> 00:12:58,450
I truly dread to imagine

245
00:12:59,200 --> 00:13:00,600
what life will be like

246
00:13:00,960 --> 00:13:02,320
for our child and me

247
00:13:02,710 --> 00:13:04,510
once she enters your household.

248
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:08,200
Zhu'er, you're worrying too much.

249
00:13:08,200 --> 00:13:09,000
Don't worry.

250
00:13:09,720 --> 00:13:10,870
After the wedding,

251
00:13:10,920 --> 00:13:12,080
I will properly bring you into the household

252
00:13:12,080 --> 00:13:13,010
as my concubine.

253
00:13:13,240 --> 00:13:14,080
With me there,

254
00:13:14,480 --> 00:13:15,440
no one will ever hurt

255
00:13:15,440 --> 00:13:16,440
you and our child.

256
00:13:22,120 --> 00:13:23,280
How dare she

257
00:13:23,280 --> 00:13:24,680
speak ill of you, My Lady?

258
00:13:24,980 --> 00:13:25,960
She's slandering

259
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:27,440
Liang Zixuan's future wife,

260
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:28,440
not me.

261
00:13:29,120 --> 00:13:30,980
Once I break off this engagement,

262
00:13:31,120 --> 00:13:33,000
she can slander whoever she wants.

263
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:35,260
It'll have nothing to do with me anymore.

264
00:13:36,370 --> 00:13:37,600
They must have left their names

265
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:38,800
on the wooden plaque.

266
00:13:39,080 --> 00:13:40,440
When I get the evidence,

267
00:13:40,640 --> 00:13:42,120
I won't fear them denying everything

268
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:43,200
when I break off the engagement.

269
00:13:43,200 --> 00:13:43,560
G...

270
00:13:44,240 --> 00:13:45,200
Great.

271
00:13:45,200 --> 00:13:45,800
It's worth it that you've been keeping

272
00:13:45,800 --> 00:13:47,660
an eye on them for such a long time.

273
00:13:47,720 --> 00:13:48,120
Come on, come on.

274
00:13:48,120 --> 00:13:48,650
Hurry up.

275
00:13:56,800 --> 00:13:57,460
Be careful.

276
00:14:05,880 --> 00:14:06,600
Suxin,

277
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:08,120
keep a good watch outside.

278
