00:28:35,920 --> 00:28:37,640
Make sure to take good care of Miss Ming.

563
00:28:37,640 --> 00:28:40,040
There mustn't be the slightest oversight.

564
00:28:42,920 --> 00:28:44,520
Miss Ming, this way, please.

565
00:28:47,040 --> 00:28:47,720
That over there is

566
00:28:47,720 --> 00:28:49,200
Miss Rong'er's quarters.

567
00:28:52,560 --> 00:28:54,530
And what about that eastern wing?

568
00:28:54,760 --> 00:28:56,020
And what's this place?

569
00:28:56,600 --> 00:28:58,720
The east side is His and Her Grace's quarters.

570
00:28:58,720 --> 00:28:59,560
This place

571
00:28:59,560 --> 00:29:01,320
is the Young Master's study.

572
00:29:02,960 --> 00:29:04,120
What's your name?

573
00:29:04,520 --> 00:29:05,380
How old are you?

574
00:29:05,560 --> 00:29:06,520
I'm Ling'er,

575
00:29:06,520 --> 00:29:07,520
17 this year.

576
00:29:07,960 --> 00:29:09,080
Ling'er...

577
00:29:10,320 --> 00:29:11,450
Looking carefully,

578
00:29:11,720 --> 00:29:13,720
you're quite a beauty in the making.

579
00:29:13,760 --> 00:29:15,420
Your skin is soft and fair too.

580
00:29:15,760 --> 00:29:17,160
Are you wearing rouge?

581
00:29:17,960 --> 00:29:19,520
No, Miss, I'm not.

582
00:29:20,160 --> 00:29:22,640
Then why are your cheeks so rosy?

583
00:29:25,560 --> 00:29:27,230
And your hands too.

584
00:29:32,800 --> 00:29:33,520
They say that hands

585
00:29:33,520 --> 00:29:34,400
are a woman's

586
00:29:34,400 --> 00:29:35,160
second face.

587
00:29:37,000 --> 00:29:38,800
I'm accustomed to daily chores,

588
00:29:38,800 --> 00:29:40,600
so my hands are naturally rough.

589
00:29:41,200 --> 00:29:42,920
They say that rosy hands indicate a prosperous fate

590
00:29:42,920 --> 00:29:45,200
that will benefit one's husband and the household.

591
00:29:45,200 --> 00:29:46,920
You and I are about the same age,

592
00:29:46,920 --> 00:29:48,320
so I imagine Her Grace will soon

593
00:29:48,320 --> 00:29:49,850
arrange a marriage for you.

594
00:29:50,400 --> 00:29:51,160
This concerns

595
00:29:51,160 --> 00:29:52,620
your lifelong happiness.

596
00:29:52,960 --> 00:29:54,720
But I have to do chores every day.

597
00:29:54,720 --> 00:29:55,520
My hands

598
00:29:55,720 --> 00:29:57,080
naturally can't compare

599
00:29:57,080 --> 00:29:58,680
to those of you young ladies.

600
00:30:00,280 --> 00:30:01,540
That's not difficult.

601
00:30:02,120 --> 00:30:03,160
I have a formula.

602
00:30:03,160 --> 00:30:05,080
If you use it consistently morning and evening,

603
00:30:05,080 --> 00:30:06,610
I guarantee that your hands

604
00:30:06,800 --> 00:30:08,530
will become delicate and fair.

605
00:30:08,560 --> 00:30:10,120
Is that true, Miss Ming?

606
00:30:10,120 --> 00:30:10,920
Absolutely.

607
00:30:11,320 --> 00:30:13,200
You just need to get motherwort,

608
00:30:13,200 --> 00:30:14,600
atractylodes, cardamom,

609
00:30:14,600 --> 00:30:15,800
and a bit of pearl powder.

610
00:30:15,800 --> 00:30:18,660
I'll teach you how to prepare the formula right now.

611
00:30:19,510 --> 00:30:20,320
B-But...

612
00:30:20,320 --> 00:30:22,250
I'll just be in Rong'er's quarters.

613
00:30:22,250 --> 00:30:24,040
After you bring the ingredients,

614
00:30:24,040 --> 00:30:24,640
I can

615
00:30:24,640 --> 00:30:25,640
prepare a batch

616
00:30:25,640 --> 00:30:26,770
for Rong'er as well.

617
00:30:27,280 --> 00:30:28,480
I'll be back soon.

618
00:31:04,930 --> 00:31:06,460
Have you cleaned the study?

619
00:31:06,840 --> 00:31:07,920
I'll be right there.

620
00:31:07,920 --> 00:31:09,040
Hurry up, hurry up!

621
00:31:14,120 --> 00:31:15,920
Hurry up, hurry up! Move faster!

622
00:31:31,680 --> 00:31:33,000
It's you.

623
00:31:34,960 --> 00:31:36,360
Sir, please show mercy.

624
00:31:36,480 --> 00:31:38,120
I am a guest in the household.

625
00:31:38,280 --> 00:31:39,200
I only entered this place

626
00:31:39,200 --> 00:31:40,400
because I lost my way.

627
00:31:40,440 --> 00:31:41,770
If I'm gone for too long,

628
00:31:41,920 --> 00:31:43,040
the household will surely become suspicious.

629
00:31:43,040 --> 00:31:43,520
At that time,

630
00:31:43,520 --> 00:31:44,520
it would bring you

631
00:31:44,520 --> 00:31:45,780
unnecessary trouble.

632
00:31:45,800 --> 00:31:47,160
Why don't you let me go?

633
00:31:47,570 --> 00:31:49,500
I promise to keep my lips sealed...

634
00:31:50,280 --> 00:31:51,760
as if we never met today.

635
00:31:51,760 --> 00:31:53,020
Only one kind of person

636
00:31:53,080 --> 00:31:55,120
can truly keep their lips sealed.

637
00:31:56,590 --> 00:31:57,580
I swear!

638
00:31:58,000 --> 00:31:59,160
As long as you let me

639
00:31:59,160 --> 00:32:00,120
go unharmed,

640
00:32:00,400 --> 00:32:01,440
I'll go back now.

641
00:32:01,640 --> 00:32:02,640
From then on, I won't leave the house

642
00:32:02,640 --> 00:32:03,520
or speak a word.

643
00:32:03,960 --> 00:32:04,920
I've never entered

644
00:32:04,920 --> 00:32:05,800
Liang's study,

645
00:32:05,960 --> 00:32:08,120
haven't seen any secret room,

646
00:32:08,120 --> 00:32:10,120
and certainly haven't seen anyone!

647
00:32:10,960 --> 00:32:12,620
Miss, your eloquent words...

648
00:32:13,530 --> 00:32:15,330
are hardly convincing.

649
00:32:16,320 --> 00:32:18,450
First, he was chased by the officials,

650
00:32:18,480 --> 00:32:20,960
and now he's sneaked into Liang's secret room.

651
00:32:20,960 --> 00:32:23,020
Looks like he's undoubtedly a thief.

652
00:32:23,760 --> 00:32:26,090
I have to find another way to deal with him.

653
00:32:28,120 --> 00:32:30,780
Your actions, I assume, are out of desperation.

654
00:32:30,800 --> 00:32:32,440
You don't want the Liang family to discover you,

655
00:32:32,440 --> 00:32:33,370
and neither do I.

656
00:32:33,840 --> 00:32:35,360
I also have my reasons

657
00:32:35,960 --> 00:32:37,400
for risking coming here.

658
00:32:38,120 --> 00:32:40,280
Since we both came here with our own purposes,

659
00:32:40,280 --> 00:32:42,340
why don't we each take what we need...

660
00:32:43,520 --> 00:32:45,320
and stay out of each other's way?

661
00:32:47,260 --> 00:32:48,270
Leave now.

662
00:32:49,890 --> 00:32:51,200
Have you searched everywhere?

663
00:32:51,200 --> 00:32:52,000
Yes.

664
00:32:52,000 --> 00:32:52,600
Both the eastern and western quarters.

665
00:32:52,600 --> 00:32:54,120
But there's no sign of Miss Ming.

666
00:32:54,120 --> 00:32:55,360
I don't know where she could've gone.

667
00:32:55,360 --> 00:32:57,000
You can't even keep track of a person.

668
00:32:57,000 --> 00:32:58,800
If the one in the main hall gets suspicious,

669
00:32:58,800 --> 00:32:59,960
and we lose Chancellor Su's trust,

670
00:32:59,960 --> 00:33:01,490
I'll hold you responsible!

671
00:33:09,010 --> 00:33:10,540
This is government silver.

672
00:33:12,000 --> 00:33:13,730
Could it be that the Duke of Ling

673
00:33:14,240 --> 00:33:16,840
has been secretly embezzling official funds?

674
00:33:17,960 --> 00:33:19,920
So you're trying to steal government silver?

675
00:33:19,920 --> 00:33:21,250
This is a serious crime.

676
00:33:21,920 --> 00:33:23,000
If you have difficulties in life,

677
00:33:23,000 --> 00:33:24,640
taking some jewelry to pawn would be enough.

678
00:33:24,640 --> 00:33:25,920
Don't risk your life for a bit more silver.

679
00:33:25,920 --> 00:33:27,400
A court case is no trivial matter.

680
00:33:27,400 --> 00:33:28,930
It's none of your business.

681
00:33:30,840 --> 00:33:33,240
If I expose this first,

682
00:33:33,600 --> 00:33:35,080
what would happen to the Liang family?

683
00:33:35,080 --> 00:33:36,610
When things get out of hand,

684
00:33:36,760 --> 00:33:37,520
Liang Zixuan will have no chance

685
00:33:37,520 --> 00:33:39,320
of marrying me.

686
00:33:43,860 --> 00:33:44,810
This matter...

687
00:33:44,920 --> 00:33:46,580
is indeed none of my business.

688
00:33:46,880 --> 00:33:48,240
Then I'll take my leave.

689
00:33:48,520 --> 00:33:49,380
Take care, sir.

690
00:33:50,320 --> 00:33:51,320
Stop right there.

691
00:33:58,060 --> 00:33:58,650
You...

692
00:34:01,040 --> 00:34:02,040
What do you want?

693
00:34:02,720 --> 00:34:03,480
What...

694
00:34:04,120 --> 00:34:05,160
do you want?

695
00:34:05,420 --> 00:34:06,680
Don't come any closer.

696
00:34:15,520 --> 00:34:17,320
This is not what you should take.

697
00:34:18,639 --> 00:34:20,280
Since we're each taking what we need,

698
00:34:20,280 --> 00:34:22,010
you have no right to interfere.

699
00:34:22,360 --> 00:34:23,080
Isn't all this silver

700
00:34:23,080 --> 00:34:24,409
enough for you to steal?

701
00:34:28,040 --> 00:34:29,760
The thing you want is not here.

702
00:34:30,520 --> 00:34:31,780
If you don't leave now,

703
00:34:31,840 --> 00:34:34,239
beware of bringing trouble upon yourself.

704
00:34:38,120 --> 00:34:39,440
A thief,

705
00:34:39,440 --> 00:34:41,080
yet so righteous?

706
00:34:41,560 --> 00:34:44,159
I've never encountered anyone quite like you.

707
00:34:50,679 --> 00:34:51,860
Aunt, why are you here?

708
00:34:51,860 --> 00:34:53,330
Where are you going?

709
00:34:53,440 --> 00:34:55,360
I've been sitting in the room for a long time

710
00:34:55,360 --> 00:34:57,490
and wished to take a walk in the garden.

711
00:34:57,720 --> 00:34:58,650
Where is Zixuan?

712
00:34:59,160 --> 00:35:01,270
I've had no appetite lately

713
00:35:01,360 --> 00:35:02,560
and wanted something sweet.

714
00:35:02,560 --> 00:35:05,040
He insisted on going out to buy me some.

715
00:35:05,380 --> 00:35:06,600
Don't go out today.

716
00:35:06,600 --> 00:35:07,960
Go back to your room and rest.

717
00:35:07,960 --> 00:35:09,360
Has something happened?

718
00:35:09,520 --> 00:35:10,600
Do not meddle

719
00:35:10,600 --> 00:35:11,680
in household matters.

720
00:35:11,680 --> 00:35:12,940
Just behave yourself.

721
00:35:20,710 --> 00:35:22,510
Don't blame me for being strict.

722
00:35:22,600 --> 00:35:23,280
I'm doing this

723
00:35:23,280 --> 00:35:24,440
for you and Zixuan.

724
00:35:26,810 --> 00:35:27,970
Aunt, rest assured.

725
00:35:28,360 --> 00:35:29,770
I know my place.

726
00:35:29,980 --> 00:35:32,120
I will definitely not cause any trouble

727
00:35:32,120 --> 00:35:33,720
for Zixuan or the household.

728
00:35:34,400 --> 00:35:35,200
You stay here

729
00:35:35,200 --> 00:35:36,370
and look after Miss Zhu'er.

730
00:35:36,370 --> 00:35:36,760
Come.

731
00:35:38,780 --> 00:35:39,610
Miss Zhu'er,

732
00:35:39,720 --> 00:35:40,980
let me help you inside.

733
00:35:57,920 --> 00:35:59,950
You plan to move all of this silver?

734
00:36:00,200 --> 00:36:01,000
How will you manage

735
00:36:01,000 --> 00:36:02,680
such a thing

736
00:36:02,730 --> 00:36:04,290
in broad daylight

737
00:36:04,600 --> 00:36:06,400
without alerting a single soul?

738
00:36:06,400 --> 00:36:07,600
Sir, if you need,

739
00:36:07,600 --> 00:36:09,000
I can create a diversion

740
00:36:09,000 --> 00:36:10,520
to make it convenient for you to act.

741
00:36:10,520 --> 00:36:12,400
I only ask for one bar of government silver.

742
00:36:12,400 --> 00:36:13,960
I won't fight for anything else.

743
00:36:13,960 --> 00:36:14,520
No need.

744
00:36:15,000 --> 00:36:16,690
Have you already come up with a plan?

745
00:36:16,690 --> 00:36:17,320
No.

746
00:36:18,280 --> 00:36:19,360
It's normal to cause alarm

747
00:36:19,360 --> 00:36:20,280
during escape.

748
00:36:20,800 --> 00:36:23,000
No one can guarantee absolute success.

749
00:36:23,240 --> 00:36:24,500
If you don't leave now,

750
00:36:24,560 --> 00:36:26,120
you'll be considered my accomplice.

751
00:36:26,120 --> 00:36:28,650
The evidence and witnesses will be complete.

752
00:36:36,320 --> 00:36:36,920
I just

753
00:36:36,920 --> 00:36:38,720
want one silver bar as evidence!

754
00:36:38,760 --> 00:36:40,120
I'm not trying to split the loot with you!

755
00:36:40,120 --> 00:36:40,760
With so much silver

756
00:36:40,760 --> 00:36:41,560
easily within your grasp,

757
00:36:41,560 --> 00:36:42,800
why are you so stingy?

758
00:36:43,080 --> 00:36:44,000
Be it...

759
00:36:45,100 --> 00:36:46,420
one bar

760
00:36:46,720 --> 00:36:47,520
or just a tael,

761
00:36:47,920 --> 00:36:49,720
you'll still be courting death.

762
00:36:50,080 --> 00:36:51,080
If you want to stay

763
00:36:51,210 --> 00:36:53,010
and bear the theft charge for me,

764
00:36:53,160 --> 00:36:54,160
I don't mind.

765
00:36:55,440 --> 00:36:56,700
Very well, I'll leave.

766
00:37:03,080 --> 00:37:03,640
Tan.

767
00:37:04,280 --> 00:37:05,280
Tan.

768
00:37:06,640 --> 00:37:07,600
Wake up.

769
00:37:07,600 --> 00:37:08,240
Tan?

770
00:37:09,240 --> 00:37:10,120
Tan?

771
00:37:11,280 --> 00:37:11,960
Minmin.

772
00:37:11,960 --> 00:37:13,220
You're finally awake.

773
00:37:13,240 --> 00:37:14,360
If you hadn't woken up,

774
00:37:14,360 --> 00:37:15,440
I was about to rush to Duke of Ling's mansion

775
00:37:15,440 --> 00:37:16,560
and make them pay.

776
00:37:20,640 --> 00:37:22,000
How did I get back?

777
00:37:22,040 --> 00:37:22,840
Your godmother,

778
00:37:22,840 --> 00:37:23,800
along with people from the Duke of Ling's household,

779
00:37:23,800 --> 00:37:24,800
sent you back.

780
00:37:24,800 --> 00:37:25,720
When Suxin and I saw

781
00:37:25,720 --> 00:37:26,720
you being carried in,

782
00:37:26,720 --> 00:37:28,240
we nearly fainted from fright.

783
00:37:28,240 --> 00:37:29,120
Luckily, the doctor said

784
00:37:29,120 --> 00:37:30,280
you only fainted

785
00:37:30,280 --> 00:37:31,240
from shock.

786
00:37:31,360 --> 00:37:32,360
Where is my godmother?

787
00:37:32,360 --> 00:37:33,440
Your godmother and the others watched over you

788
00:37:33,440 --> 00:37:34,320
for several hours.

789
00:37:34,320 --> 00:37:35,120
Seeing that you still hadn't awakened,

790
00:37:35,120 --> 00:37:36,520
they had to return first.

791
00:37:42,680 --> 00:37:44,400
Was there anything unusual in the Liang household?

792
00:37:44,400 --> 00:37:45,640
I should be the one asking you!

793
00:37:45,640 --> 00:37:46,440
How did you end up

794
00:37:46,440 --> 00:37:47,760
fainting in Liang Zixuan's study?

795
00:37:47,760 --> 00:37:48,520
Study?

796
00:37:49,080 --> 00:37:50,760
Shouldn't I have been in the secret room?

797
00:37:50,760 --> 00:37:51,400
Tan,

798
00:37:51,560 --> 00:37:52,760
did you find something?

799
00:37:52,760 --> 00:37:53,520
I did,

800
00:37:54,120 --> 00:37:55,800
but I didn't get concrete evidence.

801
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:57,660
Might as well have found nothing.

802
00:37:58,400 --> 00:38:00,440
It's all that troublemaker's fault.

803
00:38:00,440 --> 00:38:02,280
He ruined my plan many times.

804
00:38:02,480 --> 00:38:03,120
If it weren't for him,

805
00:38:03,120 --> 00:38:04,800
I would have obtained the evidence long ago.

806
00:38:04,800 --> 00:38:05,870
Troublemaker?

807
00:38:06,280 --> 00:38:07,280
Who is that?

808
00:38:10,120 --> 00:38:11,650
Let's not talk about it now.

809
00:38:11,720 --> 00:38:12,480
Suxin!

810
00:38:13,580 --> 00:38:14,840
My Lady, you're awake.

811
00:38:15,440 --> 00:38:16,280
Are you all right?

812
00:38:16,280 --> 00:38:17,840
Have our people keep a close watch on the Liang's Mansion.

813
00:38:17,840 --> 00:38:18,440
The servants

814
00:38:18,440 --> 00:38:19,600
have been watching

815
00:38:19,600 --> 00:38:20,120
as you ordered.

816
00:38:20,120 --> 00:38:21,040
Now we need to watch

817
00:38:21,040 --> 00:38:22,840
not only Liang Zixuan and Zhu'er

818
00:38:23,240 --> 00:38:24,920
but also everyone in that household.

819
00:38:24,920 --> 00:38:26,750
If anything happens,

820
00:38:26,800 --> 00:38:28,060
report to me promptly.

821
00:38:28,120 --> 00:38:28,920
Yes, My Lady.

822
00:38:32,600 --> 00:38:33,480
Tan.

823
00:38:34,240 --> 00:38:36,570
Did something happen in the Liang family?

824
00:38:37,720 --> 00:38:39,280
Nothing has happened yet,

825
00:38:39,840 --> 00:38:41,040
but that doesn't mean

826
00:38:41,040 --> 00:38:42,770
we won't be implicated by them.

827
00:38:43,120 --> 00:38:43,920
If my marriage

828
00:38:44,250 --> 00:38:45,510
isn't called off soon,

829
00:38:45,600 --> 00:38:46,560
our family

830
00:38:46,560 --> 00:38:49,090
might be implicated in trouble for no reason.

831
00:38:53,220 --> 00:38:54,730
Wait...

832
00:38:54,920 --> 00:38:56,760
Silver... where's my silver?

833
00:38:56,760 --> 00:38:59,400
How... how could this happen?

834
00:38:59,520 --> 00:39:00,180
Your Grace.

835
00:39:00,520 --> 00:39:01,850
It's Prince of Dingbei.

836
00:39:02,440 --> 00:39:04,600
The Dingbei Army is owed nearly a million taels
in unpaid military wages.

837
00:39:04,600 --> 00:39:05,720
Today, I've recovered only a fraction

838
00:39:05,720 --> 00:39:07,280
of the embezzled funds from your household.

839
00:39:07,280 --> 00:39:08,480
The rest of the accounts

840
00:39:08,480 --> 00:39:09,560
will be settled later.

841
00:39:08,550 --> 00:39:12,070
[Liang Qiwei, Duke of Ling]

842
00:39:09,640 --> 00:39:10,960
How is this possible?

843
00:39:11,120 --> 00:39:13,360
Why would the Prince of Dingbei be in the capital?

844
00:39:13,360 --> 00:39:14,240
Two years ago,

845
00:39:14,170 --> 00:39:18,480
[Zhang Ji, Scribe of the Duke of Ling's Household]

846
00:39:14,440 --> 00:39:16,720
when the former Vice Minister of Revenue
embezzled military funds,

